name: Vaporunny - the most fluffable LoRA
description:
Vaporunny - the most fluffable LoRA

This LoRA generates the vaporeon/lopunny fusion know as Vaporunny. Both fusions, vaporeon_ears and lopunny_ears, are packed into this LoRA. Works at 0.7 to 1 scale, but will vary per model.

Triggers and Example Prompt:

  • vaporunny

  • lopunny_ears or vaporeon_ears

  • white_pupils (black sclera recommended), blue_eyes (white sclera recommended), purple_eyes, and red_eyes

  • white_collar, white_fluffy_collar, or leave out for no neck features

  • fins

  • tail (as always with tails, this produces mixed results)

Example prompt:

vaporunny, vaporeon_ears, white_pupils, white_fluffy_collar, fins, 1girl, blue_skin, :3, upper body, light_blush, sleeveless_shirt, <lora:vaporunnyTheMost_full:1>

Training details

The LoRA was trained on AnyLoRA for 20 epochs using 54 images with 10 repeats. Clip skip = 2

No regularization images were used because I am not sure what dataset would work best for the Vaporunny character. Idea suggestions for a regularization dataset are welcome. A future version with regularization may preserve the base model's style better.
